Written By Kristopher Gimenez March 3rd ,2023
This block and its associated DB are used to poll the profinet network for device status.
Read the PLC local Time, HMI get the time.
Heartbeat, to get the online status of HMI. To replace DeviceStates. DeviceState does not work. Dont know why
Heartbeat is lost if state stays the same for the timeout time. Reset if Transition seen on heartbeat
Perform Device Exist check (mode 4) to see if device online
Perform Device Fault check (mode 2) to see if device has fault. Set Status as Opposite. 1 = No Fault
